Ranger Help for: journal
========================

SYNTAX:      journal/journal <quest name>
USAGE:       Any wilderness terrain.

SUMMARY:    
This command lets a Ranger flip through his or her journal of quests.
Just typing 'journal' brings up a quest list, while typing 'journal' and
a quest name brings up some info about the quest.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: stats, tally, journal, repair and glevels

